  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Temporary learning and education spaces safe for the protection of displaced children in Piura</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective is to ensure that 4,540 girls and boys of the two most affected provinces have access to education, psychosocial support in temporal spaces in safe and protective environments.  This includes temporary learning spaces and child friendly environments protecting them from violence, sexual abuse and trafficking while providing psychological support. The project will be implemented over four months.</narrative>
